quran[14{c,v,t}:
106,1,Quresh ke manoos karne ke sabab
106,2,( yani ) un ko jaray aur garmi ke safar se manoos karne ke sabab
106,3,logon ko chahiye ke ( is Nemat ke shukar mein ) is ghar ke maalik ki ibadat karen
106,4,jis ne un ko bhook mein khana khilaya aur khauf se aman bakhsha
107,1,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jo ( rozِ ) jaza ko jhutlata hai ?
107,2,"yeh wohi ( badbakht ) hai, jo yateem ko dhakkay deta hai"
107,3,aur faqeer ko khana khilanay ke liye ( logon ko ) targheeb nahi deta
107,4,to aisay nmazyon ki kharabi hai
107,5,jo namaz ki taraf se ghaafil rehtay hain
107,6,jo riya kaari karte hain
107,7,aur baratnay ki cheeze ariyatan nahi dete
108,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko kousar ataa farmai hai
108,2,to apne perwar-digaar ke liye namaz parha karo aur qurbani diya karo
108,3,kuch shak nahi ke tumhara dushman hi be aulaad rahay ga
